OL,3,CFormer PSNI officer given suspended
OL,4,Csentence for domestic abuse
OL,6,FThe Director of Foyle Women's Aid has
OL,7,Fsaid comments made by a judge during
OL,8,Fthe sentencing of a police officer
OL,9,Fsacked for domestic abuse are
OL,10,F"appalling".
OL,12,FDistrict Judge Oonagh Mullan described
OL,13,Fthe incident as "unfortunate".
OL,15,FKyle Millar was sacked from PSNI after
OL,16,Fhe admitted subjecting his former
OL,17,Fpartner to domestic abuse while he was
OL,18,Fa serving officer.
