OL,3,CFormer PSNI officer given suspended
OL,4,Csentence for domestic abuse
OL,6,FOn Friday, the 28-year-old, whose
OL,7,Faddress was given as PSNI
OL,8,FHeadquarters, Knock Road, Belfast was
OL,9,Fhanded an 8-month suspended sentence.
OL,11,FLondonderry Magistrates Court heard
OL,12,Fhis offending had a huge impact on the
OL,13,Fmental health of his victim who is
OL,14,Freceiving treatment and struggling to
OL,15,Fmove forward with her life.
