OL,3,CFormer PSNI officer given suspended
OL,4,Csentence for domestic abuse
OL,6,FIn a statement, PSNI Detective Chief
OL,7,FInspector Claire Gilbert said: "Anyone
OL,8,Fwho commits domestic abuse crimes of
OL,9,Fany nature in our community, no matter
OL,10,Fwho they are or what role they play in
OL,11,Fsociety, they will be investigated
OL,12,Fthoroughly and brought before the
OL,13,Fcourts.
OL,15,F"As a Police Service, we expect the
OL,16,Fhighest standards of professionalism
OL,17,Fand integrity from all of our police
OL,18,Fofficers, both on and off duty, in
OL,19,Faccordance with the standards
OL,20,Fcontained in the Police Service of
OL,21,FNorthern Ireland's Code of Ethics.
